value.value: Adult brain-intrinsic neuron with its soma in the brain, posterior to the antler (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It has postsynapses in the ipsilateral superior medial protocerebrum, the ipsilateral superior intermediate protocerebrum, the ipsilateral inferior bridge and the ipsilateral superior clamp (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It has presynapses in the contralateral inferior clamp, the ipsilateral superior medial protocerebrum, the contralateral superior medial protocerebrum and the contralateral inferior bridge (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 2 of these cells per organism (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024).
